dc:description: Eight pieces.  Neck and much of body broken away.  Below constriction at base of neck, body is ovoid, with widest diameter at shoulder.  Sides taper continually to bottom.  Ring base has straight flaring sides.  Concave underneath, raising vessel up somewhat.  Base has diagonal striations on upper side.  Bubbling throughout.
